Naravno.

00:26:55.231 --> 00:26:57.132
Hajdemo.

00:26:57.133 --> 00:26:58.466
Ovde ima nekih dobrih.

00:26:58.467 --> 00:26:59.902
Bailey, dođi ovamo.

