Navikni se na to.

00:55:01.649 --> 00:55:03.849
Budi jaka.

00:55:08.990 --> 00:55:10.537
Dobra devojka.

00:55:21.235 --> 00:55:22.748
Da?

00:55:27.509 --> 00:55:28.814
Šta je?

